room_title: Escape room "Sweetie: The Doctor Is In (And You Better Run)" by Lost Key Escape Rooms in Lewiston
room_description: ...Rumor has it, there is a monster, called Sweetie, created to do more than just sense fear. It feeds off terror and grows stronger with the sound of pounding heartbeats. You and your team have unknowingly been captured and are in line to become the Doctor's next specimen. He will be back for you in 1 hour, see if you can escape before it's too late, or risk becoming his permanent guinea pig! (Those afraid of blindfolds and small spaces beware!)
